反对。汀布莱克的表演是自回忆录发行以来他第二次登上舞台，也是第一次表演这首歌。</p><p>斯皮尔斯在她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/britney-spears-memoir-sells-over-one-million-copies-in-first-week-3529018">《纽约时报》畅销书中</a>将“Cry Me A River”视频描述为“一个长得像我的女人背叛了他，而他在雨中悲伤地徘徊”。</p><p>她补充说，媒体将她视为“伤了美国金童心的妓女” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/britney-spears-could-barely-speak-for-months-following-break-up-with-justin-timberlake-3520904">，而实际上，她“在路易斯安那州昏迷不醒”，试图修补她受伤的心</a>，而汀布莱克则“在好莱坞快乐地奔跑”。</p><p>这位流行歌星还透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/britney-spears-reveals-she-had-an-abortion-while-dating-justin-timberlake-3516693">她在 1998 年至 2002 年间与汀布莱克约会时堕胎</a>，因为汀布莱克认为他们“还没有准备好在我们的生活中生孩子”并且“太年轻”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C00_Nh6u0ZH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><